Title: A Kaleidoscope of Emotion
DateModified: '2019-03-08'
DatePublished: '2019-03-08'
Url: https://www.worldnomads.com/create/scholarships/writing/2019/applications/a-kaleidoscope-of-emotion
SetInCountry: Portugal
Category: Making a local connection
AuthorName: Pearse Moran
AuthorCountry: Australia
Text: When I first went to Portugal, I knew it was the bravest thing I'd ever do.
  I was like everyone else, working the regular 9-5 office job and dreaming of taking
  my dream adventure. When I arrived, the hot dusty Mediterranean air scorched my
  throat and made me parched; I couldn't wait for the first sip of wine.
